#. js-lingui-id: HP7per
#: src/pages/settings/applications/utils/getStandardApplicationDescription.ts
msgid ""
"The base data model every Twenty workspace runs on.\n"
"\n"
"#### What \"foundation\" means\n"
"\n"
"Every Twenty workspace starts with this set of objects. They define the shape of your CRM, including relationships, activity, and reporting. Everything else, including marketplace apps, AI agents, and custom objects, plugs into them.\n"
"\n"
"#### Included objects\n"
"- **People & Companies**: contact and account records\n"
"- **Opportunities**: your sales pipeline\n"
"- **Notes & Tasks**: activity and follow-ups\n"
"- **Workflows & Dashboards**: automation and reporting\n"
"\n"
"Remove this app and the rest of Twenty has nothing to hang off.\n"
"\n"
"#### Build your own app\n"
"\n"
"Extend Twenty with your own objects, fields, logic functions, or AI skills. Scaffold a new app in one command:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"npx create-twenty-app@latest my-twenty-app\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Then inside the folder:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"cd my-twenty-app\n"
"yarn twenty dev\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"See the [Getting Started guide](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/getting-started) for the full walkthrough, and [Building Apps](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/building) for the `defineApplication` / `defineEntity` APIs."
msgstr ""
"Die basiese datamodel waarop elke Twenty-werkruimte loop.\n"
"\n"
"#### Wat 'grondslag' beteken\n"
"\n"
"Elke Twenty-werkruimte begin met hierdie stel objekte. Hulle bepaal die vorm van jou Kliënteverhoudingsbestuur, insluitend verhoudings, aktiwiteit en rapportering. Alles anders, insluitend markplek-toepassings, KI-agente en pasgemaakte objekte, koppel daarby in.\n"
"\n"
"#### Ingeslote objekte\n"
"- **Mense & Maatskappye**: kontak- en rekeningrekords\n"
"- **Geleenthede**: jou verkooppyplyn\n"
"- **Notas & Take**: aktiwiteit en opvolgaksies\n"
"- **Werkvloeie & Dashboards**: outomatisering en rapportering\n"
"\n"
"Verwyder hierdie toepassing en die res van Twenty het niks om op te steun nie.\n"
"\n"
"#### Bou jou eie toepassing\n"
"\n"
"Brei Twenty uit met jou eie objekte, velde, logikafunksies of KI-vaardighede. Skep 'n nuwe toepassing met een opdrag:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"npx create-twenty-app@latest my-twenty-app\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Gaan dan binne die vouer:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"cd my-twenty-app\n"
"yarn twenty dev\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Sien die [Aan die gang-gids](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/getting-started) vir die volledige stap-vir-stapgids, en [Bou toepassings](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/building) vir die `defineApplication` / `defineEntity` API's."

